HEADWORD: Bombycinous
<hw>Bom*byc"i*nous</hw> <pr>(b⟦ocr⟧m*b⟦icr⟧s"⟦icr⟧*n⟦ucr⟧s)</pr>,
<pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>bombycinus</ets>. See
<er>Bombazine</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Silken; made of silk.</def>
